    "These aspects of AI systems have been explored in previous research, and we believe they deserve dedicated studies of their own.",
    "Beyond our core set of NLP tasks §3.2: TAXON-OMY, we recognize a broader class of frontier scenarios that lie outside the scope of FLAME's current evaluation.",
